title: Pt.1 Shimano LX M563 3 speed shifter : Dissembled Service overhaul rebuild
description: So in 1994 you had 3 models of shifter for the LX group. M560, M563 and M564. Much like the LX M564 shifters, these slightly differ. The brake levers are not removable notably, whereas from what I can remember, the M564’s are. M564’s are servo wave, whilst these are not. The M560’s had no dial indicateurs, which I prefer. In 1995, you had 4 models of LX shifters. This is part 1 of the shifter rebuild. Part 2 is the 7 speed side. I've got more bike parts than bikes! This channel gives me a reason to buy another bike part and to keep working on bikes. Une raison d'etre if you will. Please suscribe if I helped you, so I can make longer videos instead of making 2 part videos.Love bikes, components aswell as the history of cycling. Specifically 1980's and 1990's MTB's. Something about the adventure, using a 2 wheeled device that allows you to freely go where you want,  was my attraction to cycling.

Achtung: Oft versteht man Euch nicht so gut, wenn es windig ist. Dann bitte das Mikro des Handys etwas mit der Hand abdecken.b) Schicke uns Dein Video per wetransfer (https://www.wetransfer.com). Als Empfänger-Adresse info@motorradtest.de eintragen und Deine eigene EMail-Adresse nicht vergessen.c) Fertig - sobald wir das Video erhalten haben werden wir es auf unseren Kanal hochladen und Dich per EMail informieren.DANKE FÜRS MITMACHEN und viel Spaß beim Betrachten der anderen User-Bikes!

description: On October 28, alumnae, parents, students, faculty, staff, and friends came together — completely virtually — for 24 hours of paying it forward to the next generation of extraordinary Barnard women during a Giving Day unlike any other. The Barnard community has always been known for its ability to take on any challenge with spirit and devotion, but the palpable enthusiasm and love for our students were beyond impressive this year. By standing together, we soared to astounding new heights.With the goal of raising $1.2 million, Barnard set out to hit an ambitious total, and boldly succeeded by reaching  $1,835,731 and counting, from 3,556 gifts.In addition to making gifts throughout the day, the Barnard community shared their memories, photos, and love for the College on social media.This is the @BARNARDALUMNAE compiled Instagram story from this special day.LEARN MORE: barnard.edu/news/barnard-soars-new-heights-giving-day-2020
